<h2 class="wp-block-heading">What is Polygon DeFi Yield Farming: A Gateway to Liquidity Pools</h2>



<p>Yield farming on Polygon DeFi lets users join liquidity pools to boost their earnings. By adding liquidity, users can get rewards like interest, transaction fees, and tokens.</p>



