<p><a href="https://securenest.org/learn/what-is-polygon-matic">Polygon</a> hosts over 350 decentralized applications (dApps). It also has more transactions than the Ethereum network. This shows Polygon&#8217;s DeFi ecosystem is growing fast.</p>



