<h3 class="wp-block-heading">The Integral Role of MATIC in Polygon&#8217;s DeFi Landscape</h3>



<p>As the native cryptocurrency of the Polygon network, MATIC serves as the essential utility token that powers various functions within the platform&#8217;s DeFi ecosystem.</p>



<p>Its role extends across multiple layers of the Polygon network, facilitating secure and efficient transactions, powering smart contracts, and enabling decentralized applications (dApps) to thrive.</p>



