<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Smart Contracts and Scalability: The Building Blocks of Polygon&#8217;s DeFi Services</h3>



<p>Smart contracts on Polygon are built on Ethereum&#8217;s EVM, allowing for seamless interoperability with Ethereum. </p>



<p>This means that decentralized applications (dApps) and smart contracts developed for Ethereum can be easily ported to Polygon.</p>



<p>Furthermore, Polygon&#8217;s scalability solutions, such as the use of multiple side chains and the Polygon commit chain, enable high throughput and low latency for transactions, making it an ideal environment for DeFi applications.</p>



<p>This architecture ensures that the Polygon DeFi ecosystem can support a wide array of financial services without compromising on speed or cost-effectiveness, offering a truly robust infrastructure for decentralized finance.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">DeFi Protocols Flourishing Within Polygon</h3>



